  Change this:
  ```json
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "rollup --config rollup.config.js -w",
    "build": "rollup --config rollup.config.js --environment BUILD:production"
  },
  ```
  To this:
  ```json
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "rollup --config rollup.config.js -w --bundleConfigAsCjs",
    "build": "rollup --config rollup.config.js --environment BUILD:production --bundleConfigAsCjs"
  },
  ```
  (Add `--bundleConfigAsCjs` to both `dev` and `build` scripts for consistency).
